{"tid":533641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉網上直播3少主洗澡 警方於印傭手機找不到涉案片段","createTime":"2018-01-19T03:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T07:09:48.000Z","uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cffeb24e60ba382d6e1f89caa0f00969caff83cf","tid":533641,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180118/large/1516257601_76a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180118%2Flarge%2F1516257601_76a7.jpg&h=e3e44d6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印傭涉於facebook直播3名少主洗澡而被捕，被控發佈兒童色情物品罪。惟案件今再提訊時，控方表示已完成針對被告手機的調查工作，稱找不到涉案裸體影片，亦找不到其他裸體照片及影片，但指由於被告曾上載涉案影片至facebook，故現正聯絡facebook，案件押後至3月1日再訊，以便警方繼續調查及諮詢律政司意見。<br />\n<br />\n被告獲准以1,500元現金保釋，需每天到灣仔警署報到，期間不得騷擾控方證人及到案發地點。被告離開法院時以手遮擋記者鏡頭，並說「唔好影我！做咩影我！」。<br />\n控罪指被告Yuni Kristiani（28歲）去年12月1日在北角城市花園一單位內，用手提電話發佈一段含有3名兒童X、Y、Z的兒童色情物品到facebook。據悉，受害兒童有男有女，年齡由5至7歲。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180118/57722720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57722720&d=gOWvjm7v2wDT3Waua6LgiP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b8bae69f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57722720&h=8ac4a040\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180118/57722720</a>"},{"pid":"b8eec420437fc2ee8fc2adb8360e626395568af0","tid":533641,"uid":10031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:17:50.000Z","msg":"直播有record?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e334d3ed970f38b3fc2df3917e9057e84fe8658","tid":533641,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcac383ac94d863d9a53a66140b6115895b7